headline: Costco Stock Today: This Bear Put Spread Could Earn Up To $1,300 By November
summary: Shares of Costco Wholesale have lost their shine this year.  On Monday, Costco stock traded down 1% for the year while the S&P 500 has climbed nearly 15%.  Investors who expect further weakness in Costco stock can use an options bear put spread to express this view.

headline: Publix, Disney, Google, Apple and Costco, Florida’s Most Reputable Companies per Merco
summary: MIAMI, October 06, 2025--Merco, a leading corporate reputation monitor with a 25-year track record, today announced the first edition of Merco Companies and Business Leaders Rankings in the sunshine state. Merco’s multi-stakeholder evaluation methodology is also the only KPMG-verified corporate reputation assessment in the world.
